                <div class="menu-item-label">Pumpkin Juice{Star Juice}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="~/images/Screenshot 2024-10-02 183142.png" alt="Peach">
                <div class="menu-item-label">Beverages</div>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="~/images/Food.png" alt="Poké Bowls">
                <div class="menu-item-label">Food</div>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="~/images/Packs.png" alt="Food">
                <div class="menu-item-label">Smoothies</div>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="~/images/Grab n Go.png" alt="Grab & Go">
                <div class="menu-item-label">Grab & Go</div>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="~/images/Fresh Juice.png" alt="Fresh Juice Shots">
                <div class="menu-item-label">Fresh Juice </div>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="~/images/Bowls.png" alt="Merchandise">
                <div class="menu-item-label">Bowls</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="client">
        <h1 style="color: #ff6347;">WHAT OUR CLIENTS ARE SAYING</h1>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="~/images/phoebe.jpg" width="40px" height="220" class="card-img-top" alt="Client 1">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Jumbo Juice has the best smoothies in town! The Mango Magic is my absolute favorite. The staff is always friendly and the service is quick. Highly recommend!<br /> - Rachel G.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        Rachel G.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="~/images/rachel.jpg" width="40px" height="220" class="card-img-top" alt="Client 2">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>I love the variety of fresh juices at Jumbo Juice. The Green Detox is a must-try. The ambiance is great, and it's a perfect spot to relax and enjoy a healthy drink.<br /> - Monica G.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        Monica G.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="~/images/monica.jpg" width="40px" height="220" class="card-img-top" alt="Client 3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Jumbo Juice never disappoints! The Berry Blast smoothie is delicious and refreshing. 
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        Phoebe B.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>


    

   
